General.Name: FORCS Co.Ltd
General.Description: FORCS Co.,Ltd. provides enterprise e-form and reporting solutions in South Korea and internationally. The company offers OZ e-Form, an electronic form solution to collect, distribute, and manage data conveniently; and OZ Report, a web-based reporting solution to support business life cycles from distributions to operations, and is involved in creating business reports, such as dashboards, scorecards, and gantt charts. It also provides eformsign, an e-Form SaaS (Software-as-a-service) for small businesses to take processes online to speed up daily activities. In addition, the company serves clients in the banking, insurance, government, manufacturing, telecommunications, automotive, healthcare, food and beverages, education, and human resources industries. FORCS Co.,Ltd was founded in 1995 and is based in Seoul, South Korea.
